      </h2>
      <p
        class="lead text-md-center mb-4"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="200"
        data-aos-duration="1400"
      >
        Get to know the dedicated residents who lead our community.
      </p>
      <div class="row g-4 mb-4">
        <div
          class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"
          data-aos="flip-up"
          data-aos-delay="100"
          data-aos-duration="1400"
        >
          <div class="card card-lift border h-100 position-relative">
            <div class="card-body">
              <span
                class="position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-4 badge text-body bg-secondary-subtle border fs-6"
              >
                President
              </span>
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5 mb-3">James Mitchell</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                James has lived in Longhorn Heights for over a decade and brings a strong background
                in leadership.
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-1">
                <i class="ri-mail-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-muted text-decoration-none"
                  >hello@email.com</a
                >
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                <i class="ri-phone-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="tel:1234567890" class="text-muted text-decoration-none">(123) 456-7890</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"
          data-aos="flip-up"
          data-aos-delay="200"
          data-aos-duration="1400"
        >
          <div class="card card-lift border h-100 position-relative">
            <div class="card-body">
              <span
                class="position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-4 badge text-body bg-secondary-subtle border fs-6"
              >
                Vice President
              </span>
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5 mb-3">Robert Hayes</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                Robert is passionate about neighborhood safety and sustainability initiatives in the
                Austin area.
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-1">
                <i class="ri-mail-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-muted text-decoration-none"
                  >hello@email.com</a
                >
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                <i class="ri-phone-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="tel:1234567890" class="text-muted text-decoration-none">(123) 456-7890</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"
          data-aos="flip-up"
          data-aos-delay="300"
          data-aos-duration="1400"
        >
          <div class="card card-lift border h-100 position-relative">
            <div class="card-body">
              <span
                class="position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-4 badge text-body bg-secondary-subtle border fs-6"
              >
                Treasurer
              </span>
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5 mb-3">William Carter</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                William oversees the HOA's finances and works to ensure responsible and transparent
                budgeting.
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-1">
                <i class="ri-mail-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-muted text-decoration-none"
                  >hello@email.com</a
                >
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                <i class="ri-phone-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="tel:1234567890" class="text-muted text-decoration-none">(123) 456-7890</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"
          data-aos="flip-up"
          data-aos-delay="400"
          data-aos-duration="1400"
        >
          <div class="card card-lift border h-100 position-relative">
            <div class="card-body">
              <span
                class="position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-4 badge text-body bg-secondary-subtle border fs-6"
              >
                Secretary
              </span>
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5 mb-3">David Anderson</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                David manages records and communication for the HOA, keeping residents informed and
                engaged.
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-1">
                <i class="ri-mail-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-muted text-decoration-none"
                  >hello@email.com</a
                >
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                <i class="ri-phone-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="tel:1234567890" class="text-muted text-decoration-none">(123) 456-7890</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"
          data-aos="flip-up"
          data-aos-delay="500"
          data-aos-duration="1400"
        >
          <div class="card card-lift border h-100 position-relative">
            <div class="card-body">
              <span
                class="position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-4 badge text-body bg-secondary-subtle border fs-6"
              >
                Management
              </span>
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5 mb-3">John Bennett</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                John helps coordinate neighborhood events and brings a fresh perspective to
                community projects.
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-1">
                <i class="ri-mail-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-muted text-decoration-none"
                  >hello@email.com</a
                >
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                <i class="ri-phone-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="tel:1234567890" class="text-muted text-decoration-none">(123) 456-7890</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="col-md-6 col-lg-4"
          data-aos="flip-up"
          data-aos-delay="600"
          data-aos-duration="1400"
        >
          <div class="card card-lift border h-100 position-relative">
            <div class="card-body">
              <span
                class="position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-4 badge text-body bg-secondary-subtle border fs-6"
              >
                Management
              </span>
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5 mb-3">Michael Brooks</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                Michael serves as the bridge between residents and the board, focusing on outreach
                and inclusion.
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-1">
                <i class="ri-mail-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-muted text-decoration-none"
                  >hello@email.com</a
                >
              </p>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                <i class="ri-phone-fill me-2"></i>
                <a href="tel:1234567890" class="text-muted text-decoration-none">(123) 456-7890</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a
          href="#"
          class="btn btn-lg btn-primary"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="700"
          data-aos-duration="1400">Contact the Board<i class="ri-arrow-right-line ms-2"></i></a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Community Committees Section -->
  <section class="bg-body pt-3 pb-5">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="fs-1 text-md-center mb-2" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1400">
        Community Committees
      </h2>
      <p
        class="lead text-md-center mb-4"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="200"
        data-aos-duration="1400"
      >
        Our committees are the heart of resident involvement at Longhorn Heights.
      </p>

      <div class="row g-4">
        <!-- Architectural Review Committee -->
        <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="flip-up" data-aos-delay="100" data-aos-duration="1400">
          <div class="card card-lift border h-100 position-relative">
            <span
              class="badge text-body bg-secondary-subtle border fs-6 position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-4"
              >5 Members</span
            >
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5">Architectural Review</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                Ensures that all home modifications and construction comply with community standards
                and HOA guidelines.
              </p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled text-muted mb-2">
                <li><strong>Chair:</strong> Dana Keller</li>
                <li><strong>Meets:</strong> 1st Thursday of each month</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-decoration-none text-muted">
                <i class="ri-mail-line me-1"></i>hello@email.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Landscaping Committee -->
        <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="flip-up" data-aos-delay="200" data-aos-duration="1400">
          <div class="card card-lift border h-100 position-relative">
            <span
              class="badge text-body bg-secondary-subtle border fs-6 position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-4"
              >7 Members</span
            >
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5">Landscaping</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                Focuses on the upkeep of green spaces, seasonal planting, and overall neighborhood
                beautification projects.
              </p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled text-muted mb-2">
                <li><strong>Chair:</strong> Miguel Alvarez</li>
                <li><strong>Meets:</strong> Quarterly</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-decoration-none text-muted">
                <i class="ri-mail-line me-1"></i>hello@email.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Social & Events Committee -->
        <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="flip-up" data-aos-delay="300" data-aos-duration="1400">
          <div class="card card-lift border h-100 position-relative">
            <span
              class="badge text-body bg-secondary-subtle border fs-6 position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-4"
              >6 Members</span
            >
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5">Social & Events</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                Plans and organizes neighborhood events including block parties, holiday
                celebrations, and community meetups.
              </p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled text-muted mb-2">
                <li><strong>Chair:</strong> Jenna Thomas</li>
                <li><strong>Meets:</strong> Monthly</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-decoration-none text-muted">
                <i class="ri-mail-line me-1"></i>hello@email.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Safety & Security Committee -->
        <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="flip-up" data-aos-delay="400" data-aos-duration="1400">
          <div class="card card-lift border h-100 position-relative">
            <span
              class="badge text-body bg-secondary-subtle border fs-6 position-absolute top-0 end-0 m-4"
              >4 Members</span
            >
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5">Safety & Security</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                Works to keep Longhorn Heights safe by coordinating with local authorities and
                promoting community awareness.
              </p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled text-muted mb-2">
                <li><strong>Chair:</strong> Brian Grant</li>
                <li><strong>Meets:</strong> Every other month</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-decoration-none text-muted">
                <i class="ri-mail-line me-1"></i>hello@email.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Management Company Section -->
  <section class="bg-body pt-3 pb-5">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="fs-1 text-md-center mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1400">
        Management Company
      </h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div
          class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-3"
          data-aos="zoom-in"
          data-aos-delay="200"
          data-aos-duration="1400"
        >
          <div class="card border">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title fs-5">Lone Star Property Management</h5>
              <p class="card-text">
                Longhorn Heights is proudly managed by <strong>Lone Star Property Management</strong
                >, a locally based firm with extensive experience supporting Austin-area
                communities.
              </p>

              <div class="mb-3">
                <h6>Contact Information</h6>
                <p class="mb-1 text-muted">
                  <i class="ri-mail-fill text-primary me-2"></i>
                  <a href="mailto:hello@email.com" class="text-muted text-decoration-none"
                    >hello@email.com</a
                  >
                </p>
                <p class="mb-1 text-muted">
                  <i class="ri-phone-fill text-primary me-2"></i>
                  <a href="tel:2345678901" class="text-muted text-decoration-none">(234) 567-8901</a
                  >
                </p>
                <p class="mb-0 text-muted">
                  <i class="ri-map-pin-line text-primary me-2"></i>
                  1234 Heritage Parkway, Suite 200, Austin, TX 78701
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="mb-3">
                <h6>Office Hours</h6>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                  Monday – Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM<br />
                  Closed on weekends and public holidays
                </p>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h6>Website</h6>
                <a href="#" target="_blank" class="text-primary text-decoration-none">
                  www.example.com
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-body pt-3 pb-5">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1400">
          <h2 class="fs-1 mb-3">Get Involved</h2>
          <p class="lead mb-4">
            Longhorn Heights thrives because of residents like you. Whether it's joining a
            committee, attending an event, or volunteering your skills, there's a place for everyone
            to contribute.
          </p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary">Join a Committee</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
